          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Ridge Valley school brings and nurtures the unique talent of each and every child . The environment given to the child to grow and develop is what every parent craves for. Being a parent i can totally feel the gradual positive change in my child, the increase in his confidence, his leadership skills and his way of dealing with peers, seniors and juniors is something I should admire.  To feel it one should visit it and experience it.",
          "publisher": {
